# {{ name }}

Generated by `okpf init --template software-onboarding`.

- `artifacts/setup.md`, `artifacts/architecture.md`, `artifacts/troubleshooting.md`
  — replace with real project docs.
- `records/decisions.jsonl` — structured knowledge records (one JSON object
  per line). Add more with a text editor, or via `okpf add`.
- `provenance/sources.json` — where the source material came from.
- `evals/onboarding-questions.json` — questions used to check whether the
  pack actually teaches what it claims to.

Run `okpf validate .` from this directory before sharing the pack.

See `examples/software-onboarding/` in the OKPF repository for a fully
filled-out reference version of this template.
